{"tid":1704970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可能係你保命/拒絕死得不明不白- 大叫師","createTime":"2019-11-10T23:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T23:51:59.000Z","uid":2113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3a63f0372b9f534f53338320e7d8529886c20560","tid":1704970,"uid":2113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T23:42:15.000Z","msg":"我發現左有問題 就係<br />\n永遠啲人只係會叫 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">啊！救命！</span></span><br />\n或者<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔夠大聲聽唔到名</span><br />\n應該詳細咁叫：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">救命啊+<br />\n警察/防暴/速龍/便衣 +<br />\n地方+<br />\n發生乜事<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n<br />\n救命啊 警察入屋拉人啊！<br />\n<br />\n救命啊 有警察係公園拉人啊<br />\n<br />\n每一句句子都可以<strong>方便到街坊去救你</strong><br />\n亦可以<strong>留底證據</strong><br />\n<br />\n然後有個最大問題 <br />\n就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">叫得唔夠大聲/叫口號叫到聲沙</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 平時一定要大叫</span>：<br />\n啊，甴曱啊 <br />\n啊，有蟲啊<br />\n我愛你啊<br />\n或者十點叫口號<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好再咁博命叫口號啦！！<br />\n叫到聲沙 不如 1 2 3 做野<br />\n留返把聲保命"},{"pid":"b469877bf2a26756be0f0844ad530246e2fac359","tid":1704970,"uid":2113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T23:51:59.000Z","msg":"推"}]}